expression.expression: CASE WHEN ERSDA = '00000000' THEN CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE To_timestamp(ERSDA,'yyyyMMdd') END
CASE WHEN LAEDA = '00000000' THEN CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE To_timestamp(LAEDA,'yyyyMMdd') END
CASE WHEN MSTDE = '00000000' THEN CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE To_timestamp(MSTDE,'yyyyMMdd') END
CASE WHEN MSTDV = '00000000' THEN CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP) ELSE To_timestamp(MSTDV,'yyyyMMdd') END
CASE WHEN length(REPLACE(trim(EAN_UPC),' ','')) = 0 THEN '' ELSE Concat(Substring('00000000000000',1,14-length(REPLACE(trim(EAN_UPC),' ',''))),REPLACE(trim(EAN_UPC),' ','')) END
